# COBOL Orchestrator Backend

- Keep orchestrator work additive under `src/omnix/orchestrator/cobol/`.
- Do not modify the COBOL runner, gates, receipt schema, fabric providers, runtime capture layer, Studio frontend, find-bugs, or scan pipeline for this slice.
- Keep terminal decisions explicit: missing fixtures, unresolved copybooks, budget warnings, and exhausted Gate 6 retries must be visible to the operator.
- Persist run state under `.omnix/runs/<run_id>/state.db`.
- Use stdlib plus existing OMNIX modules only.
- Receipt schema is locked; orchestrator metadata belongs in run state and audit summaries.
- Tests for this backend live under `tests/cobol/orchestrator/S<N>/`.

